944f4e0%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia%20is%20a%20flawed%20but%20thriving%20democracy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20the%20world's%20largest%20democracy.%20Its%20first%20elections%20were%20held%20in%201951-52%20after%20it%20gained%20independence%20from%20Britain.%20Free%20elections%20have%20been%20held%20in%20nearly%20every%20election%20cycle%20since%2C%20with%20a%20coup%20in%201975%20briefly%20threatening%20India's%20democratic%20status.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20a%20rare%20bright%20spot%20in%20a%20world%20where%20democracy%20seems%20to%20be%20in%20retreat.%20Even%20in%20the%20US%2C%20the%20global%20champion%20of%20democracy%2C%20former%20president%20Donald%20Trump%20is%20accused%20of%20launching%20an%20attempt%20to%20cling%20to%20power%20illegally%20after%20losing%20the%202020%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Indian%20voters%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6662fd4ecc442a2f676efd9b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIndian%20newspaper%20sellers%20queue%20to%20collect%20papers%20to%20sell%20the%20morning%20after%20the%20country's%20general%20election%20results%20were%20announced%20on%20June%205%2C%202024%2C%20in%20New%20Delhi.%3Cp%3ERebecca%20Conway%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia%20isn't%20a%20perfect%20democracy%20but%20it%20is%20still%20a%20role%20model%20for%20developing%20nations%2C%20large%20or%20small.%20And%20given%20trends%20in%20some%20Western%20democracies%2C%20I%20would%20have%20to%20say%20that%20there%20are%20several%20things%20they%2C%20too%2C%20should%20be%20learning%20from%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jabin%20T.%20Jacob%2C%20an%20expert%20on%20India-China%20relations%20at%20Shiv%20Nadar%20University%2C%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIndia's%20democracy%2C%20though%2C%20faces%20a%20stern%20test%20under%20Modi%2C%20say%20critics.%20Global%20democracy%20watchdog%20%3Ca%20h