to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fuber-lyft-driving-single-mom-low-earners-gig-work-flexibility-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Equit%20their%20gigs%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20and%20others%20to%20push%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fuber-lyft-leave-minneapolis-drivers-pay-minimum-wage-earnings-ordinance-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ehigher%20guaranteed%20pay%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20drivers%20told%20BI%20they%20increasingly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-much-tip-lyft-uber-drivers-tipping-doordash-gig-economy-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erely%20on%20tips%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20especially%20when%20some%20drivers%20are%20growingly%20reporting%20rides%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fuber-lyft-pay-tips-minimum-wage-driving-gig-work-expenses-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eat%20or%20below%20%243%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20asked%20gig%20economy%20experts%20and%20drivers%20why%20food%20delivery%20drivers%20get%20more%20generous%20tips%20than%20ride-hailing%20drivers%2C%20what's%20preventing%20some%20people%20from%20tipping%2C%20and%20what%20Uber%20and%20Lyft%20could%20do%20to%20boost%20customer%20tips.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2257771d2d-4bcf-475c-80e4-3e06c7b90aef%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHistorical%20tipping%20norms%2C%20inflation%2C%20and%20high%20ride%20prices%20can%20influence%20tips%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECarla%20Bevins%2C%20an%20associate%20professor%20of%20business%20management%20at%20Carnegie%20Mellon%20University%2C%20thinks%20food%20delivery%20drivers%20are%20more%20likely%20to%20get%20tips%20than%20ride-hailing%20drivers%20because%20tipping%20for%20food-related%20services%20has%20%26quot%3Blong%20been%20a%20part%20of%20American%20culture.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20contrast%2C%20rideshare%20services%2C%20though%20equally%20valuable%2C%20do%20not%20have%20the%20same%20historical%20tipping%20expectation%20and%20are%20often%20viewed%20as%20more%20transactional%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20BI%20via%20email.%20For%20both%20ride-hailing%20and%20food%20delivery%2C%20she%20said%20the%20digital%20tipping%20process%20via%20phone%20reduces%20the%20social%20pressure%20to%20tip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20ride-hailing%20drivers%20said%20they%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fuber-driver-tipping-trends-getting-worse-taylor-swift-riders-best-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enoticed%20tipping%20declining%3C%2Fa%3E%20throughout%20the%20pandemic.%20Some%20said%20inflation%20may%20have%20eaten%20away%20at%20many%20passengers'%20wallets%2C%20making%20them%20less%20likely%20to%20tip%2C%20while%20others%20said%20people's%20appreciation%20of%20essential%20workers%20through%20generous%20tipping%20has%20withered%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOthers%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fuber-lyft-tips-tipping-culture-gig-work-delivery-drivers-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eblamed%20the%20companies%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20noting%20that%20passengers%20may%20be%20less%20likely%20to%20leave%20an%20additional%20tip%20as%20ride%20prices%20increase.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDeborah%2C%20who%20takes%20multiple%20Uber%20or%20Lyft%20rides%20a%20day%2C%20said%20as%20fares%20increase%2C%20it's%20more%20challenging%20to%20dig%20into%20her%20pockets%20and%20give%20generous%20tips%20%E2%80%94%20though%20she%20still%20tips%20on%20every%20ride.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20of%20us%20are%20everyday%20workers%20and%20employees%20living%20from%20paycheck%20to%20paycheck.%20We%20have%20families%20and%20children%20to%20feed%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20Deborah%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20the%20major%20ride-hailing%20and%20food%20delivery%20companies%20argue%20that%20tipping%20is%20robust%20and%20on%20the%20rise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%2C%20Uber%20told%20BI%20that%20over%20the%20last%20four%20years%2C%20ride-hailing%20tipping%20frequency%20and%20the%20average%20tip%20size%20have%20both%20roughly%20doubled%20%E2%80%94%20adding%20that%20the%20average%20ride-hailing%20tip%20amount%20rose%20nearly%2010%25%20over%20the%20past%20six%20months.%20For%20food%20delivery%20orders%2C%20the%20average%20tip%20amount%20increased%20roughly%2035%25%20over%20the%20past%20six%20months%2C%20the%20company%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUber%20said%20this%20is%20because%20of%20changes%20to%20the%20app%20that%20encourage%20tipping.%20This%20includes%20allowing%20passengers%20to%20tip%20during%20the%20trip%20and%20moving%20the%20tip%20selection%20prompt%20above%20the%20ratings%20prompt.%20For%20Uber%20Eats%2C%20suggested%20tip%20amounts%20vary%20based%20on%20order%20size%2C%20and%20customers%20are%20reminded%20of%20inclement%20weather%20to%20encourage%20tipping.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20second%20half%20of%202023%2C%20Lyft%20said%20the%20median%20US%20Lyft%20driver%20earned%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lyft.com%2Fblog%2Fposts%2Fdriver-net-earnings%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%2431%20per%20hour%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20engaged%20time%20%E2%80%94%20when%20they%20were%20en%20route%20to%20pick%20up%20a%20passenger%20or%20had%20one%20in%20their%20vehicle.%20The%20company%20said%20these%20earnings%20included%20a%20median%20tip%20of%20%242.41%20per%20engaged%20hour.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Lyft%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lyft.com%2Fblog%2Fposts%2Fthe-united-states-of-tipping-when-and-where-riders-tip-most%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eanalysis%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20passenger%20tipping%20published%20last%20July%20found%20that%20airport%20pickups%20and%20dropoffs%20%26quot%3Bresulted%20in%20twice%20as%20many%20tips%20as%20non-airport%20trips.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDoorDash%20said%2080%25%20of%20Dashers%20have%20other%20income%20sources%2C%20and%2090%25%20spend%20under%2010%20hours%20weekly%20on%20delivery.%20Still%2C%20DoorDash%20said%20it's%20encouraging%20tips%20through%20in-app%20notifications%20for%20customers%2C%20warning%20them%20that%20their%20food%20may%20take%20longer%20to%20arrive%20if%20they%20refuse%20to%20tip.%20The%20vast%20majority%20of%20customers%20tip%2C%20DoorDash%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20notification%20pilot%20resulted%20in%20significantly%20fewer%20%240%20tips.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDashers%20go%20above%20and%20beyond%20everyday%20for%20their%20communities%2C%20which%20is%20why%20we've%20made%20it%20easier%20than%20ever%20for%20customers%20to%20show%20their%20appreciation%20by%20leaving%20a%20tip%20at%20checkout%2C%20during%20delivery%2C%20or%20up%20to%2030%20days%20after%20delivery%20%E2%80%94%20all%20directly%20in%20the%20DoorDash%20app%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20DoorDash%20spokesperson%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229b2b228a-7637-47ee-8f27-9555b96d7474%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EUber%20and%20Lyft%20drivers%20rarely%20get%20tips%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESteve%2C%20who%20asked%20to%20use%20a%20pseudonym%20for%20fear%20of%20professional%20repercussions%2C%20has%20driven%20for%20over%20five%20years%20in%20Los%20Angeles%20and%20said%20he's%20been%20increasingly%20reliant%20on%20tips.%20Some%20days%2C%20he%20waits%20one%20or%20two%20hours%20before%20getting%20a%20ride%20going%20his%20direction%2C%20so%20he%20said%20tips%20are%20helpful%20to%20make%20up%20for%20dead%20periods.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20tips%20are%20few%20and%20far%20between%2C%20even%20when%20he%20offers%20good%20service%20and%20helps%20passengers%20with%20luggage.%20He%20suspects%20one%20of%20the%20reasons%20for%20low%20tipping%20rates%20is%20that%20years%20ago%2C%20Uber%20did%20not%20encourage%20tips.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Uber%20first%20started%2C%20there%20was%20no%20tipping%20option.%20In%202016%2C%20Uber's%20public%20policy%20team%20noted%2C%20%26quot%3Bwe%20felt%20it%20would%20be%20better%20for%20riders%20and%20drivers%20to%20know%20for%20sure%20what%20they%20would%20pay%20or%20earn%20on%20each%20trip%20%E2%80%94%20without%20the%20uncertainty%20of%20tipping.%26quot%3B%20Uber%20further%20wrote%20tipping%20was%20%26quot%3Bnot%20included%2C%20nor%20is%20it%20expected%20or%20required.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20Uber%20has%20added%20in-app%20tipping%20and%20provided%20a%20simpler%20tipping%20interface%2C%20Steve%20said%20many%20people%20may%20still%20be%20conditioned%20to%20not%20tip%20ride-hailing%20drivers.%20He%20added%20the%20lack%20of%20tips%20has%20been%20%26quot%3Bdemoralizing%2C%26quot%3B%20leading%20him%20to%20reject%20more%20rides%20and%20consider%20pivoting%20to%20another%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EErskien%20Lenier%2C%2066%2C%20is%20about%20to%20quit%20driving%20for%20Uber%20and%20Lyft%20and%20pivot%20to%20freelance%20diet%20and%20fitness%20coaching.%20The%20Riverside%2C%20California-based%20driver%20started%20almost%20nine%20years%20ago%20after%20working%20long%20hours%20in%20the%20car%20industry.%20While%20he%20could%20make%20%242%2C000%20to%20%243%2C00%20a%20week%20pre-pandemic%2C%20he%20now%20struggles%20to%20make%20above%20%24900%20a%20week%20working%20similar%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he's%20recently%20received%20more%20tips%20than%20ever%20before%2C%20sometimes%20%2450%20to%20%2460%20a%20day%2C%20from%20starting%20engaging%20conversations%20with%20passengers%20about%20his%20passions%20for%20health%20and%20fitness.%20He%20said%20he%20has%20more%20control%20over%20receiving%20tips%20with%20Uber%20X%20than%20Uber%20Eats%2C%20where%20he%20doesn't%20interface%20with%20the%20customer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20try%20to%20set%20myself%20with%20the%20mindset%20of%20I'm%20out%20here%20to%20have%20a%20good%20time%2C%20make%20some%20money%2C%20make%20some%20friends%2C%20and%20get%20home%20safe%2C%26quot%3B%20Lenier%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20his%20tip%20amounts%20have%20fallen%20with%20his%20earnings%2C%20and%20it's%20not%20sustainable%2C%20especially%20as%20he%20gets%20older.%20So%20far%20this%20week%2C%20he's%20made%20%24567.17%2C%20only%20%2430.68%20of%20which%20came%20from%20tips.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222aabcf40-e359-46ac-b273-dcc9e2369612%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ETipping%20isn't%20so%20smooth%20for%20delivery%20drivers%2C%20either%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAlex%2C%20a%20DoorDash%20driver%20in%20Texas%2C%20said%20he%20only%20takes%20orders%20that%20will%20give%20decent%20tips.%20Sometimes%2C%20this%20means%20refusing%20to%20complete%20a%20delivery%20if%20he%20predicts%20he'll%20get%20a%20bad%20review%2C%20which%20could%20hurt%20tips.%20In%20the%20last%2030%20days%2C%20he%20said%20his%20acceptance%20rate%20fluctuated%20between%2020%25%20and%2030%25%20while%20maintaining%20a%204.9%20customer%20rating%20and%2098%25%20completion%20rate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20estimates%20two-thirds%20of%20his%20income%20comes%20from%20tipping%2C%20noting%20that%20he%20would%20not%20be%20able%20to%20survive%20on%20base%20pay%20alone.%20While%20he%20gets%20tips%20on%20most%20rides%2C%20he%20said%20he's%20dealt%20with%20tip%20baiting%20%E2%80%94%20when%20people%20take%20their%20tips%20away%20after%20he%20accepts%20the%20orders.%20He's%20also%20seen%20more%20%241%20tips%20after%20DoorDash%20implemented%20its%20notification%20pilot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20taken%20him%20a%20few%20months%20to%20figure%20out%20the%20best%20strategies%20for%20maximizing%20tips%2C%20such%20as%20driving%20later%20at%20night%20when%20there's%20less%20competition%20and%20traffic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226ced646d-a16c-459f-9e23-2a7a7cd331f0%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20Uber%20and%20Lyft%20can%20influence%20driver%20tips%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EErin%20Hatton%2C%20a%20professor%20of%20sociology%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Buffalo%2C%20told%20BI%20via%20email%20that%20ride-hailing%20companies%20can%20%26quot%3Bstrongly%20influence%20tipping%20practices%20by%20setting%20standard%20tipping%20amounts%20in%20the%20app%20for%20customers%20to%20choose%20from.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrice%20hikes%20can%20also%20discourage%20tipping.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDuring%20surge%20pricing%20on%20Uber%2C%20for%20example%2C%20a%20customer%20could%20think%20twice%20about%20adding%20a%20tip%20on%20top%20of%20an%20already%20increased%20fare%2C%26quot%3B%20Carnegie%20Mellon's%20Bevins%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBevins%20said%20that%20the%20perception%20of%20gig%20driver%20pay%2C%20driven%20by%20various%20factors%20such%20as%20media%20coverage%2C%20could%20impact%20how%20much%20people%20tip.%20The%20more%20people%20think%20they're%20reliant%20on%20tips%2C%20the%20more%20generous%20they%20might%20be%20likely%20to%20be.%20She%20said%20Uber%20and%20Lyft%20can%20do%20more%20to%20raise%20awareness%20about%20the%20impact%20tips%20can%20have%20on%20drivers%20through%20educational%20campaigns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20recommendations%20included%20reminding%20passengers%20during%20checkout%20that%20%26quot%3B100%25%20of%20your%20tip%20goes%20to%20your%20driver%26quot%3B%20and%20reminding%20customers%20to%20tip%20immediately%20after%20the%20ride.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20some%20gig%20drivers%2C%20there's%20a%20lot%20at%20stake%20over%20the%20future%20of%20tipping.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20for%20any%20tipped%20employee%20%E2%80%94%20but%20particularly%20those%20who%20are%20not%20guaranteed%20a%20minimum%20wage%2C%20let%20alone%20a%20living%20wage%20%E2%80%94%20tips%20are%20a%20crucial%20source%20of%20income%2C%26quot%3B%20Hatton%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAre%20you%20a%20gig%20driver%20who%20is%20struggling%20to%20make%20ends%20meet%3F%20Reach%20out%20to%20these%20reporters%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ansheidlower%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Ensheidlower%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20or%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ajzinkula%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Ejzinkula%40businessin