card-future-of-india-after-lok-sabha-polls-124060800370_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Felections%2Flok-sabha-election%2Fcongress-reviews-scorecard-future-of-india-after-lok-sabha-polls-124060800370_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Felections%2Flok-sabha-election%2Fcongress-reviews-scorecard-future-of-india-after-lok-sabha-polls-124060800370_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Maratha%20Reservation%20Activist%20Manoj%20Jarange%20Begins%20Fast%20Unto%20Death%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMaratha%20reservation%20activist%20Manoj%20Jarange%20Patil%20started%20his%20fast%20unto%20death%20today%20as%20indicated%20by%20him%20in%20April%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20officials%2C%20the%20Police%20have%20not%20permitted%20him%20for%20the%20indefinite%20fast.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Patil%20said%20that%20if%20the%20Maratha%20reservation%20is%20not%20provided%20this%20time%2C%20he%20will%20contest%20the%20Maharashtra%20Assembly%20elections%20that%20are%20expected%20to%20take%20place%20in%20October%20later%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20April%20this%20year%2C%20Mr%20Patil%20said%20that%20he%20would%20go%20on%20a%20hunger%20strike%20if%20the%20state%20government%20did%20not%20resolve%20the%20Maratha%20reservation%20issue%20by%20June%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20had%20criticized%20both%20the%20ruling%20Mahyuti%20tripartite%20alliance%20and%20the%20opposition%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20for%20%26quot%3Bdoing%20nothing%26quot%3B%20regarding%20the%20Maratha%20reservation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20been%20misled%20by%20the%20state%20government.%20Mahayuti%20has%20not%20given%20us%20Maratha%20reservation...When%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20was%20in%20power%2C%20they%20did%20nothing%20for%20the%20Maratha%20reservation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Maratha%20community%20had%20been%20protesting%20against%20the%20state%20government%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20the%20Maratha%20reservation%20for%20several%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20February%20this%20year%2C%20the%20Maharashtra%20government%2C%20during%20a%20special%20assembly%20session%2C%20approved%20a%20Bill%20to%20extend%2010%20per%20cent%20reservation%20to%20the%20Marathas%2C%20based%20on%20a%20report%20submitted%20by%20the%20Maharashtra%20Backward%20Class%20Commission%20(MBCC).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Patil%20had%20earlier%20in%20February%20this%20year%20ended%20his%20hunger%20strike%20against%20the%20government%20after%2017%20days.%20However%2C%20Jarange%20Patil%20opposed%20the%20reservation%20and%20insisted%20on%20a%20quota%20for%20the%20Marathas%20under%20the%20OBC%20category.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJarange%20Patil's%20Maratha%20reservation%20campaign%20is%20accused%20of%20receiving%20financial%20support%20from%20'political%20associates%2C'%20and%20it%20is%20alleged%20that%20he%20made%20inflammatory%20remarks%20during%20the%20campaign.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Patil%20had%20claimed%20that%20Maharashtra%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20was%20conspiring%20to%20eliminate%20him%20(Manoj%20Patil)%20by%20poisoning%20him%20with%20saline.%20In%20a%20reply%20to%20the%20Manoj%20Patil%20claim%2C%20Maharashtra%20BJP%20Chief%20Ashish%20Shelar%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWhatever%20Manoj%20Jarange%20Patil%20says%2C%20he%20is%20making%20false%20allegations%2C%20he%20is%20misleading%20the%20people.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20March%2C%20in%20sign%20of%20taking%20a%20tougher%20stand%20against%20the%20Maratha%20agitation%2C%20the%20Maharashtra%20government%20constituted%20a%20Special%20Investigation%20Team%20(SIT)%20to%20investigate%20the%20allegations%20of%20conspiracy%20and%20violence%20during%20the%20stir%20in%20Maharashtra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SIT%20was%20formed%20on%20the%20instructions%20of%20the%20Maharashtra%20assembly%20speaker%20after%20the%20matt