p%3EThe%20coalition%20negotiations%20are%20a%20throwback%20to%20an%20era%20before%202014%20-%20when%20PM%20Modi%20swept%20to%20power%20with%20an%20outright%20BJP%20majority%20-%20in%20which%20alliance%20partners%20haggled%20for%20positions%20and%20benefits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBuzz%20of%20a%20sensational%20Nitish%20Kumar%20-%20INDIA%20bloc%20reunion%20surfaced%20Tuesday%20evening%20after%20it%20became%20clear%20the%20BJP%20would%20not%20win%20272%20seats%20on%20its%20own.%20Senior%20INDIA%20leaders%2C%20including%20ex-Maharashtra%20Chief%20Minister%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%2C%20suggested%20an%20olive%20branch%20might%20be%20extended%20to%20Nitish%20Kumar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%20sources%20close%20to%20Nitish%20Kumar%20ruled%20out%20this%20possibility%2C%20but%20left%20a%20sting%20in%20the%20tail%3B%20with%20both%20sides%20locked%20in%20talks%20over%20ministerial%20berth%20allocation%2C%20the%20BJP%20brass%20was%20reportedly%20told%20to%20remember%20Nitish%20Kumar%20had%20walked%20out%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20over%20delays%20in%20naming%20him%20as%20its%20Convenor.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717838760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-12%2Fa6nbuie_nitish-kumar-lalan-singh-_625x300_11_December_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnitish-kumars-party-to-get-2-cabinet-berths-in-modi-3-0-sources-5845020%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%20will%20be%20getting%20two%20portfolios%20in%20the%20new%20cabinet%20led%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20sources%20within%20the%20party%20said.%20The%20party%20has%20proposed%20the%20name%20of%20two%20senior%20leaders%20-%20Lalan%20Singh%20and%20Ram%20Nath%20Thakur.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnitish-kumars-party-to-get-2-cabinet-berths-in-modi-3-0-sources-5845020%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2F