egularities%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fexplainer-what-is-the-controversy-surrounding-neet-ug-2024-results-5838160%5C%22%3ENational%20Eligibility-cum-Entrance%20Test-Undergraduate%20(NEET%20UG)%3C%2Fa%3E%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaintaining%20that%20the%20exam%20was%20conducted%20with%20brief%20integrity%20and%20fair%20procedure%2C%20K%20Sanjay%20Murthy%2C%20secretary%2C%20Higher%20Education%2C%20assured%20that%20there%20was%20no%20compromise%20in%20administering%20the%20medical%20entrance%20exam.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnswering%20a%20question%20on%20whether%20the%20NTA%20would%20conduct%20the%20NEET%20UG%202024%20for%20the%20second%20time%2C%20Mr%20Murthy%20responded%2C%20%26quot%3BA%20committee%20has%20been%20formed%20to%20analyse%20the%20issue%20of%20the%20irregularities.%20Nearly%2023%20lakh%20students%20appeared%20in%20the%20exam.%20Of%20these%2C%20only%201%2C600%20candidates%20who%20took%20the%20exam%20in%20six%20centres%20have%20been%20affected%20with%20the%20controversy.%20We%20are%20still%20examining%20on%20whether%20to%20hold%20the%20exam%20again%20or%20not.%20A%20Grievance%20Redressal%20Committee%20will%20share%20the%20finding%20post%20which%20a%20decision%20will%20be%20taken.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOnly%20one%20question%20was%20challenged%20this%20year%2C%20which%20is%20the%20least%20in%20the%20history%20of%20NEET%20exams.%20Revised%20marks%20of%20many%20students%20remained%20in%20the%20negative%20even%20after%20compensation%20of%20the%20results.%20This%20reflects%20that%20compensation%20of%20marks%20have%20not%20made%20any%20difference%20in%20the%20overall%20results%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20results%20for%20the%20NEET%20UG%202024%20have%20been%20marred%20by%20various%20controversies%20of%20paper%20leak%20and%20other%20anomalies.%20There%20have%20been%20a%20total%20of%20around%2067%20students%20who%20secured%20the%20AIR%20rank%201%20this%20year.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnNEET%20is%20conducted%20for%20students%20who%20want%20to%20seek%20admission%20to%20undergraduate%20courses%20in%20medical%20and%20dental%20colleges%20across%20India.%20The%20test%20was%20conducted%20on%20May%205%2C%20and%20the%20provisional%20answer%20key%20was%20released%20on%20May%2029.%20The%20final%20answer%20key%20was%20released%20on%20June%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717838700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fprgp4jto_neet-ug-_625x300_28_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fpanel-formed-to-analyse-whether-to-hold-neet-again-education-ministry-5845222%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Education%20Ministry%20noted%20that%20the%20compensation%20of%20marks%20have%20not%20made%20any%20difference%20in%20the%20overall%20results.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fpanel-formed-to-analyse-whether-to-hold-neet-again-education-ministry-5845222%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fpanel-formed-to-analyse-whether-to-hold-neet-again-education-ministry-5845222%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fpanel-formed-to-analyse-whether-to-hold-neet-again-education-ministry-5845222%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Delhi%20On%20High%20Alert%20For%20PM%20Modi's%20Swearing-In%20Tomorrow%3A%2010%20Points%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20will%20take%20oath%2C%20as%20too%20will%20members%20of%20his%20new%20cabinet%2C%20tomorrow%20evening%20at%20the%20Rashtrapati%20Bhawan%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%20He%20will%20be%20the%20first%20three-term%20Prime%20Minister%20since%20Congress%20stalwart%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EA%20three-layered%20security%20has%20been%20put%20in%20place%20at%20Rashtrapati%20Bhawan%20where%20he%20will%20be%20administered%20oath%20of%20office%20by%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu.%20Officials%20said%20commandos%20from%20Delhi%20Police's%20SWAT%20and%20NSG%20will%20be%20deployed%20around%20the%20venue%20and%20other%20strategic%20locations%20as%20Delhi%20remains%20on%20high%20alert%20for%20the%20event.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EPolice%20have%20declared%20the%20national%20capital%20a%20no-fly%20zone%2C%20banning%20the%20use%20of%20aerial%20platforms%20like%20drones%2C%20para%20gliders%2C%20remotely%20piloted%20aircraft%20and%20hot%20air%20balloons%20for%20the%20next%20couple%20of%20days.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20swearing-in%20ceremony%20is%20expected%20to%20witness%20the%20presence%20of%20leaders%20from%20neighbouring%20countries%2C%20including%20Bangladesh%2C%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20Bhutan%2C%20Nepal%2C%20Mauritius%2C%20and%20Seychelles%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20the%20Maldives%2C%20as%20part%20of%20India's%20'Neighbourhood%20First'%20policy.%20The%20dignitaries%20will%20be%20given%20designated%20routes%20from%20their%20hotels%20to%20the%20venue%20and%20back.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EOfficials%20said%20several%20roads%20heading%20towards%20the%20central%20Delhi%20will%20be%20shut%20tomorrow%20or%20there%20may%20be%20traffic%20diversions.%20Checking%20of%20vehicles%20entering%20the%20national%20capital%20has%20already%20been%20increased.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EPM%20Modi's%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20-%20which%20claimed%20282%20seats%20in%202014%20and%20303%20in%20the%202019%20election%20won%20240%20seats%20this%20time%20-%2032%20short%20of%20the%20272-majority%20mark.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20support%20of%20incoming%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Chandrababu%20Naidu's%2016%20TDP%20MPs%20and%20the%2012%20from%20the%20JDU%20of%20his%20Bihar%20counterpart%2C%20Nitish%20Kumar%2C%20are%20seen%20as%20critical%20to%20ensuring%20the%20BJP%20can%20form%20and%20run%20its%20government%20for%20the%20full%20five%20years.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20spotlight%20is%20now%20on%20negotiations%20between%20the%20BJP%20and%20its%20two%20key%20allies%20-%20TDP%20and%20JD(U)%20-%20each%20of%20which%20is%20batting%20for%20plum%20posts%20at%20the%20Centre.%20Maharashtra%20Chief%20Minister%20Eknath%20Shinde's%20Shiv%20Sena%20faction%20and%20the%20LJP%20of%20Chirag%20Paswan%20are%20also%20seeking%20key%20portfolios%20in%20the%20new%20cabinet%20led%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20defied%20exit%20pollsters%20to%20mount%20a%20real%20challenge%20to%20the%20BJP%20in%20a%20national%20election%20-%20a%20first%20since%20the%20'Modi%20wave'%20swept%20it%20to%20power%20in%202014.%20The%20opposition%20alliance%20finished%20with%20232%20seats%20-%2040%20short%20of%20the%20272-majority%20mark.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Congress%2C%20which%20led%20the%20INDIA%20opposition%20bloc%20in%20this%20election%2C%20finished%20with%2099%20wins%20from%20the%20328%20seats%20it%20contested.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717838520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fc0rrepv8_pm-modi-pti-_625x300_07_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-narendra-modis-swearing-in-delhi-on-high-alert-for-pm-modis-swearing-in-tomorrow-10-points-5845172%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Security%20has%20been%20tightened%20in%20Delhi%20for%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20swearing-in%20tomorrow%20for%20a%20record%20third%20term.%20Special%20arrangements%20have%20also%20been%20made%20for%20the%20world%20leaders%20attending%20the%20grand%20ceremony.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-narendra-modis-swearing-in-delhi-on-high-alert-for-pm-modis-swearing-in-tomorrow-10-points-5845172%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Opinion%3A%20Eye%20On%20China%20As%20India%20Invites%20Regional%20Partners%20At%20NDA%20Sweari