ary%20pact%20with%20Beijing%2C%20which%20allows%20for%20the%20provision%20of%20Chinese%20military%20assistance%20free%20of%20charge%20to%20foster%20stronger%20bilateral%20ties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20February%20this%20year%2C%20a%20Chinese%20research%20vessel%2C%20the%20Xian%20Yang%20Hong%2003%2C%20docked%20in%20Male%2C%20a%20move%20with%20clear%20military%20implications%20for%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20China%20insists%20its%20vessels%20are%20deployed%20for%20peaceful%20purposes%2C%20India's%20Navy%20Chief%20Admiral%20Hari%20Kumar%2C%20who%20recently%20retired%2C%20had%20told%20NDTV%20that%20the%20Navy%20is%20concerned%20that%20these%20vessels%20are%20charting%20underwater%20regions%20and%20''may%20have%20military%20applications%20as%20well%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20ability%20to%20deploy%20submarines%20or%20operate%20submarines.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%20already%20operates%20a%20military%20facility%20in%20Djibouti%20on%20the%20Horn%20of%20Africa%2C%20its%20first%20international%20base.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchinas-indian-ocean-base-in-djibouti-fully-operational-warship-docked-in-satellite-pics-3264696%5C%22%3ESatellite%20imagery%20reveals%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20base%20is%20now%20fully%20operational%2C%20with%20key%20warships%20docked%20at%20newly%20constructed%20piers%20large%20enough%20to%20berth%20aircraft%20carriers%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20counters%20this%20Chinese%20base%20with%20a%20facility%20on%20the%20Mauritian%20island%20of%20Agalega.%20Construction%20on%20the%20island%20and%20reports%20of%20the%20presence%20of%20Indian%20military%20personnel%20indicate%20that%20this%20may%20become%20a%20permanent%20forward%20base%2C%20though%20neither%20Mauritius%20nor%20India%20openly%20speaks%20about%20future%20plans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecent%20images%20indicate%20the%20presence%20of%20new%20jetties%20with%20an%20upgrade%20to%20the%20airstrip%20on%20the%20island%2C%20which%20is%20being%20extended.%20It%20is%20believed%20that%20Agalega%20would%20ultimately%20base%20Indian%20Navy%20P-8%20maritime%20reconnaissance%20aircraft%2C%20a%20key%20asset%20to%20track%20Chinese%20naval%20activity%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%20east%2C%20in%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20New%20Delhi%20has%20been%20working%20hard%20to%20balance%20China's%20active%20infrastructure%20activity%20on%20the%20island.%20In%20August%202022%2C%20New%20Delhi%20objected%20to%20the%20Chinese%20deployment%20of%20the%20Yang%20Wang%2005%2C%20a%20state-of-the-art%20missile%20and%20satellite%20tracking%20vessel%2C%20to%20Hambantota%2C%20a%20Sri%20Lankan%20deep-water%20port.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EColombo%2C%20which%20had%20cleared%20China's%20development%20of%20the%20port%2C%20has%20since%20lost%20control%20of%20its%20ownership%20as%20a%20result%20of%20indebtedness%2C%20with%20a%20Chinese%20company%20having%20taken%20ownership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndian%20companies%20are%20now%20playing%20an%20increasingly%20important%20role%20in%20Sri%20Lanka's%20infrastructure%20development%2C%20in%20key%20projects%20which%20have%20also%20been%20backed%20by%20the%20United%20States%2C%20a%20key%20strategic%20partner%20for%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20November%20last%20year%2C%20the%20US%20International%20Development%20Finance%20Corporation%20committed%20%24533%20million%20(Rs.4%2C600%20crore)%20to%20finance%20Colombo%20port's%20West%20Container%20Terminal%20project.%20India's%20Adani%20group%20holds%20a%2051%25%20stake%20in%20the%20terminal.%20The%20US%20financing%20is%20expected%20to%20drastically%20expand%20the%20terminal's%20shipping%20capacity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20separate%20part%20of%20the%20same%20port%20has%20a%20terminal%20operated%20by%20China%20Merchants%20Port%20Holdings%2C%20a%20sign%20of%20Beijing's%20continued%20focus%20on%20Sri%20Lanka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20China%20has%20engaged%20several%20Indian%20Ocean%20rim%20nations%20through%20economic%20partnerships%20an