keptically%2C%20and%20I%20am%20not%20in%20a%20position%20to%20guess%20how%20likely%20it%20is%20that%20we'll%20soon%20be%20in%20a%20nuclear%20war%20with%20China%20over%20data%20centers%2C%20as%20he%20suggests.%20But%20there's%20something%20about%20his%20verbose%20proclamations%20that%20ring%20to%20me%20as%20hype.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmaxread.substack.com%2Fp%2Fwho-is-leopold-aschenbrenner%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMax%20Read%20on%20Substack%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20a%20very%20astute%20assessment%20of%20the%20manifesto%20and%20how%20the%20hyperbole%20of%20AI%20doomerism%20might%20be%2C%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20self-serving%20hype%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Csection%3EWhat%20I%20do%20know%20is%20that%20the%20Silicon%20Valley%20investor%20class%20has%20become%20quite%20contemptuous%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feffective-altruism-how-started-how-its-going-after-ftx-collapse-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEffective%20Altruism%3C%2Fa%3E%20(the%20school%20of%20thought%20that%20drove%20the%20Future%20Fund)%2C%20and%20highly%20skeptical%20and%20suspicious%20of%20the%20associated%20focus%20on%20existential%20risk%20or%20%26quot%3Bx-risk%26quot%3B%20now%20that%20it%20seems%20to%20be%20a%20retardant%20on%20their%20ambitions.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20that%20same%20class%20is%20quite%20hawkish%20on%20China%20and%20bullish%20on%20national%20security%20businesses%20and%20the%20military-industrial%20complex.%20If%20I%20were%20a%20young%20and%20ambitious%20person%20whose%20career%20so%20far%20was%20largely%20in%20%26quot%3BA.I.%20safety%26quot%3B%20and%20other%20E.A.-associated%20fields%2C%20I%20might%20attempt%20to%20re-frame%20my%20experience%20and%20interests%20as%20more%20national-security%20oriented.%20And%20if%20I%20were%20really%20trying%20to%20suck%20up%20to%20reactionary%20venture%20capitalists%20I%20might%20also%20imply%20that%20I%20was%20unjustly%20fired%20over%20unfair%20charges%20of%20racism%20by%20a%20devious%20H.R.%20drone.%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EWhile%20the%20specifics%20of%20this%20C.V.%20are%20credibility-building%20among%20Aschenbrenner's%20target%20audience%20(investors%20and%20founders%20in%20whose%20companies%20he'd%20like%20to%20invest%2C%20as%20well%20as%20dupes%20on%20Twitter%20who%20will%20boost%20his%20profile)%2C%20just%20as%20important%20is%20the%20image%20he%20fits%3A%20Young%2C%20prodigious%2C%20confident%2C%20fast-talking%2C%20able%20to%20speak%20fluidly%20on%20a%20range%20of%20subjects%20from%20geopolitics%20to%20epidemiology%20to%20chip%20design.%20If%20Aschenbrenner%20weren't%20a%20Zoomer%20I'd%20call%20him%20a%20millennial%20ambition%20psycho%3B%20certainly%2C%20he%20shares%20with%20the%20Ivy%20League%20sociopaths%20of%20my%20generation%20a%20cloying%2C%20manic%20self-assurance%20that%20somehow%20scans%20as%20%26quot%3Bgenius%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20credulous%20and%20the%20powerful%20and%20as%20%26quot%3Bextremely%20annoying%20bullshit%26quot%3B%20to%20literally%20anyone%20else.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20then%2C%20tragically%2C%20there%20is%20the%20sad%20tale%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyoutuber-mkbh-dtrashes-humane-ai-pin-firestorm-over-damage-startup-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHumane%20AI%20Pin%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Humane's%20founders%20were%20former%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EApple%3C%2Fa%3E%20employees%2C%20incredibly%20stylish%20dressers%2C%20and%20produced%20incredibly%20cool%20demo%20videos%20that%20made%20the%20product%20seem%20amazing.%20They%20raised%20%24240%20million%20from%20investors%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-mess-concerns-over-nda-safety-sam-altman-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESam%20Altman%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20first%20started%20taking%20preorders%2C%20I%20wrote%20about%20how%20I%20thought%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhumane-ai-pin-wont-replace-your-iphone-smartphone-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20Pin%20looked%20awesome%20and%20I%20wanted%20one%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20even%20if%20I%20could%20see%20how%20it%20might%20be%20slightly%20impractical.%20It%20was%20futuristic%2C%20fun%2C%20and%20made%20by%20really%20cool%20and%20edgy%20people%20%E2%80%94%20the%20ultimate%20AI%20hypesters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhumane-explores-sale-difficult-wearables-launch-ai-pin-billion-valuation-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20Pin%20has%20been%20a%20failure%3C%2Fa%3E%20so%20far.%20Early%20reviews%20were%20dreadful%2C%20sales%20were%20far%20lower%20than%20projections%2C%20and%20the%20company%20was%20criticized%20for%20launching%20a%20half-baked%20product.%20This%20week%2C%20they%20announced%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2024%2F6%2F5%2F24172377%2Fhumane-ai-pin-battery-case-issue-warning%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecall%20on%20the%20chargers%3C%2Fa%3E%20because%20there%20was%20a%20danger%20they%20could%20catch%20on%20fire.%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20laugh%20(I%20will%20not%20suggest%20that%20you%20just%20squeeze%20the%20AI%20out%20of%20it%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjuicero-offers-refund-for-squeezing-juice-packets-2017-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJuicero%3C%2Fa%3E)%20because%20I%20think%20it's%20genuinely%20a%20huge%20bummer.%20I'd%20love%20for%20an%20ambitious%20new%20kind%20of%20hardware%20device%20to%20be%20successful%3B%20I'm%20rooting%20for%20that%20to%20happen%20out%20there%20in%20the%20world%20because%20I%20love%20cool%20new%20gadgets.%20But%20this%20clearly%20just%20wasn't%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20this%20moment%2C%20in%20June%20of%202024%2C%20everyone%20knows%20AI%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bbig%20deal%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20most%20people%20don't%20know%20exactly%20what%20that%20will%20really%20%3Cem%3Emean%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20%3Cem%3Elook%20like%3C%2Fem%3E.%20This%20leaves%20the%20door%20wide%20open%20for%20hype%20purveyors%20to%20sell%20people%20on%20its%20magic%20and%20power%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0or%20play%20to%20their%20worst%20fears.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20isn't%20necessarily%20bad%20%E2%80%94%20hype%20can%20be%20useful%20just%20like%20personality%20hires%20in%20a%20workplace%20are%20useful.%20And%20the%20most%20beautiful%20part%20of%20all%20of%20this%3F%20A%20personality%20hire%20is%20the%20most%20%3Cem%3Ehuman%3C%2Fem%3E%20thing%20%E2%80%94%20something%20AI%20could%20never%20replace.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-personality-hire-openai-ai-chatgpt-why-2024-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717837621000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F666343c2ed9a404d829bc148%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-personality-hire-openai-ai-chatgpt-why-2024-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22AI%20is%20a%20field%20where%20hype%20is%20everything%2C%20and%20the%20personality%20hire%20reigns%20supreme.%20Just%20look%20at%20OpenAI's%20Sam%20Altman.%20He's%20the%20ultimate%20hype%20man.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22knotopoulos%40businessinsider.com%20(Katie%20Notopoulos)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-personality-hire-openai-ai-chatgpt-why-2024-6%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Turkey%20imposes%2040%25%20tariff%20on%20vehicle%20imports%20from%20China%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717837480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-110817490%2Cimgsize-28278.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatim