Fox%20calls%20this%20the%20%26quot%3Bprecision%20paradox.%26quot%3B%20Or%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20incongruence%20between%20precision%20strike%20theory%20and%20the%20fervent%20enthusiasm%20of%20precision%20ideologues%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20in%20an%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Frusi.org%2Fexplore-our-research%2Fpublications%2Frusi-journal%2Fprecision-paradox-and-myths-precision-strike-modern-armed-conflict%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eessay%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20for%20the%20Royal%20United%20Services%20Institute%2C%20a%20British%20think%20tank.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPrecision%20warfare%20is%20associated%20today%20with%20guided%20missiles%2C%20but%20the%20concept%20dates%20back%20to%20the%201930s%2C%20when%20the%20US%20began%20to%20embrace%20high-altitude%20daylight%20bombing%20by%20heavy%20bombers%20such%20as%20the%20B-17%20Flying%20Fortress.%20Swayed%20by%20Italian%20airpower%20theorist%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.h-net.org%2Freviews%2Fshowpdf.php%3Fid%3D42478%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EGiulio%20Douhet%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20American%20planners%20were%20convinced%20they%20could%20cripple%20an%20adversary%20by%20bombing%20its%20factories%2C%20without%20the%20need%20for%20a%20costly%20ground%20war.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20contrasted%20with%20Britain's%20night%20area-bombing%20strategy%20in%20World%20War%20II%20that%20targeted%20entire%20German%20cities.%20Even%20if%20factories%20weren't%20hit%2C%20residential%20neighborhoods%20would%20be%20destroyed%20and%20workers%20%26quot%3Bde-housed%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20was%20expected%20to%20collapse%20the%20public's%20morale.%20In%20practice%2C%20the%20distinction%20between%20precision%20and%20area%20bombardment%20proved%20blurry%3A%20bombing%20through%20cloudy%20European%20skies%20that%20obscured%20targets%2C%20while%20under%20fighter%20and%20flak%20attack%20and%20relying%20on%20pencil-on-paper%20navigation%20plotting%20and%20rudimentary%20bomb%20sights%20meant%20the%20majority%20of%20American%20bombs%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.airandspaceforces.com%2Farticle%2F1008daylight%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Efailed%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20hit%20their%20target.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPGMs%20were%20supposed%20to%20solve%20this%20problem.%20Why%20drop%20a%20dozen%20bombs%20when%20a%20single%20GPS-guided%20missile%20can%20destroy%20a%20bridge%20or%20a%20command%20post%3F%20Fox%20sees%20several%20flaws%20in%20modern%20precision%20strike%20theory.%20For%20one%2C%20%26quot%3Bdecapitation%26quot%3B%20strikes%20intended%20to%20defeat%20an%20enemy%20by%20eliminating%20its%20leaders%20and%20command%20posts%20have%20not%20worked.%20Nor%20does%20Fox%20believe%20that%20the%20precision%20strike%20strategy%20has%20actually%20shortened%20wars.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20most%20significantly%2C%20Fox%20questions%20the%20essence%20of%20US%20precision%20warfare%3A%20the%20belief%20that%20smart%20bombs%20spare%20a%20need%20for%20boots%20on%20the%20ground.%20%26quot%3BAccurate%20strikes%20are%20not%20equivalent%20to%20effective%20strikes%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20a%20strike%20can%20land%20on%20the%20intended%20area%2C%20selected%20based%20on%20intelligence%2C%20and%20yet%20fail%20to%20achieve%20the%20goal%20of%2C%20say%2C%20killing%20a%20militant%20leader%20or%20stopping%20a%20factory%20from%20making%20more%20bombs%2C%20hence%20necessitating%20follow-on%20strikes.%20When%20PGMs%20don't%20accomplish%20the%20mission%2C%20%26quot%3Bthen%20precision-based%20warfighting%20requires%20additional%20strikes%20and%2C%20likely%2C%20a%20subsequent%20use%20of%20land%20force%20activities%20to%20offset%20the%20shortcomings%20of%20precision%20strikes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22More%20than%20half%20of%20the%20buildings%20in%20Gaza%20have%20been%20damaged%20or%20destroyed%20in%20Israel's%20bombing%20campaign%20since%20the%20Oct.%207%20terror%20attacks.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66622fea1cd3b17790443378%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMore%20than%20half%20of%20the%20buildings%20in%20Gaza%20have%20been%20damaged%20or%20destroyed%20in%20Israel's%20bombing%20campaign%20since%20the%20Oct.%207%20terror%20attacks.%3Cp%3EDoaa%20Albaz%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20can%20actually%20result%20in%20higher%20civilian%20casualties%20than%20if%20conventional%20weapons%20had%20been%20used%20in%20the%20first%20place%20because%20it%20requires%20repeated%20attacks.%20%26quot%3BIf%20precision%20strikes%20are%20often%20accurate%2C%20but%20ineffective%2C%20and%20additional%20strikes%20or%20land%20operations%20are%20required%20to%20create%20the%20effect%20intended%20with%20the%20initial%20precision%20strikes%2C%20then%20precision%20strategies%20do%20not%20decrease%20civilian%20casualties%20and%20collateral%20damage%20in%20conflict%20zones.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFox%20points%20to%20the%20extensive%20use%20of%20American%20PGMs%20during%20the%20ferocious%20battles%20of%20Raqqa%20and%20Mosul%20in%202016-2017.%20In%20trying%20to%20root%20out%20heavily%20fortified%20Islamic%20State%20positions%20dug%20into%20civilian%20neighborhoods%2C%20many%20buildings%20were%20destroyed%20and%20thousands%20killed.%20Israel%20faces%20a%20similar%20situation%20today%20as%20it%20hunts%20Hamas%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThus%20the%20paradox%3A%20an%20individual%20PGM%20may%20be%20more%20accurate%20than%20a%20dumb%20bomb.%20But%20if%20a%20PGM%20fails%20to%20knock%20out%20a%20target%20%E2%80%94%20whether%20due%20to%20poor%20intelligence%20or%20the%20pure%20chance%20that%20reigns%20on%20battlefields%20%E2%80%94%20more%20guided%20weapons%20have%20to%20be%20launched%2C%20thus%20defeating%20the%20whole%20purpose%20of%20precision.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BAccurate%20strikes%20do%20not%20inherently%20mean%20effective%2C%26quot%3B%20Fox%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BTherefore%2C%20more%20strikes%20are%20required%20when%20a%20strike%20does%20not%20effectively%C2%A0accomplish%20its%20intended%20purpose.%20Thus%2C%20in%20the%20aggregate%2C%20if%20a%20PGM%20isn't%20100%20percent%20effective%2C%20it%20can%20often%20result%20in%20similar%20outcomes%20to%20ballistic%20artillery%2C%20or%20other%20non-precision%20munition%20employment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFox%20doesn't%20believe%20that%20smarter%20bombs%20will%20solve%20the%20paradox.%20%26quot%3BBetter%20PGMs%20isn't%20really%20the%20problem%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BPGMs%20are%20currently%20about%20as%20accurate%20as%20can%20be.%20For%20that%20matter%2C%20although%20artillery%20is%20an%20area%20fire%20weapon%2C%20it%20is%20still%20very%20accurate.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20what%20about%20the%20conflicts%20in%20Ukraine%20and%20Gaza%2C%20in%20which%20massive%20amounts%20of%20PGMs%20are%20being%20employed%3F%20In%20Ukraine%2C%20both%20sides%20are%20using%20massive%20numbers%20of%20guided%20weapons%2C%20at%20a%20rate%20that%20is%20depleting%20stockpiles%20and%20factory%20capacity%2C%20yet%20neither%20side%20has%20managed%20to%20achieve%20decisive%20results.%20Israel%20carried%20out%20strikes%20in%20Gaza%20against%2029%2C000%20targets%20in%20the%20first%20four%20months%20of%20the%20war%2C%20often%20with%20guided%20weapons%2C%20but%20that%20has%20failed%20so%20far%20to%20destroy%20Hamas.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BThe%20lesson%20is%20that%20Hamas%20is%20a%20land%20force%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Fox.%20%26quot%3BThe%20inconvenient%20truth%20about%20war%20is%20that%20it%20still%20requires%20a%20land%20force%20to%20defeat%20a%20land%20force.%20Precision%20warfare%2C%20which%20isn't%20really%20a%20thing%2C%20augments%20a%20land%20force%20in%20defeating%20another%20land%20force.%20It%20doesn't%20replace%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3EMichael%20Peck%20is%20a%20defense%20writer%20whose%20work%20has%20appeared%20in%20Forbes%2C%20Defense%20News%2C%20Foreign%20Policy%20magazine%2C%20and%20other%20publications.%20He%20holds%20an%20MA%20in%20political%20science%20from%20Rutgers%20Univ.%20Follow%20him%20on%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitter.com%2F%40mipeck1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3ETwitter%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fin%2Fmipeck%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3ELinkedIn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-military-confidence-smart-bombs-may-have-a-fatal-flaw-2024-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717837201000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6662300bd0b8e1c832ccdaef%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-military-confidence-smart-bombs-may-have-a-fatal-flaw-2024-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Precision%20warfare%20appeals%20to%20America's%20strengths%2C%20but%20a%20retired%20US%20Army%20officer%20argues%20that%20its%20effectiveness%20is%20a%20myth.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Michael%20Peck)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-military-confidence-smart-bombs-may-have-a-fatal-flaw-2024-6%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22IND%20vs%20PAK%20T20%20WC%20Ticket%20Price%3A%20Rs%201.46%20Crore%20Seat%20Listed%20On%20Resale%20Market%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIs%20there%20something%20magical%20about%20Seat%2030%20in%20Row%2020%20of%20Section%20252%20at%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%20stadium%20in%20East%20Meadow%3F%20The%20ticket%20for%20that%20seat%20for%20Sunday's%20India-Pakistan%20match%20has%20been%20listed%20for%20%24175%2C400%20(Rs%201.46%20crore)%20on%20the%20resale%20market%2C%20Stubhub%2C%20where%20tickets%20for%20entertainment%20and%20sports%20events%20can%20be%20legally%20sold%20with%20markups.%20It%20doesn't%20mean%20that%20the%20ticket%20will%20be%20sold%20at%20that%20price%20%E2%80%93%20it's%20just%20the%20price%20that%20the%20seller%20wants.%20Compounding%20the%20mystery%20of%20that%20high%20price%2C%20tickets%20in%20adjacent%20rows%20in%20Section%20252%2C%20were%20listed%20for%20far%20less%3A%20%24693%20in%20Row%2021%20and%20%24801%20in%20Row%2019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20ticket%20for%20a%20seat%20in%20that%20section%2C%20without%20disclosing%20the%20seat%20or%20row%20number%20is%20also%20listed%20on%20another%20resale%20site%2C%20Viagogo%2C%20for%20that%20same%20price%2C%20perhaps%20by%20the%20same%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20clamour%20for%20the%20hard-to-get%20tickets%20for%20the%20clash%20of%20neighbours%2C%20which%20many%20fans%20consider%20the%20high%20point%20of%20the%20month-long%20tournament%20spread%20over%20venues%20across%20the%20US%20and%20the%20Caribbean%20has%20spawned%20profiteering%20on%20the%20resale%20markets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20Friday%20night%2C%20a%20few%20tickets%20were%20still%20available%20on%20the%20official%20International%20Cricket%20Council%20(ICC)%20site%20without%20markups%20and%20were%20priced%20between%20%241%2C500%20in%20the%20Boundary%20Club%20section%20and%20%2410%2C000%20in%20the%20Diamond%20Club%20section.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBetween%20them%20were%20Premium%20Club%20Lounge%20section%20tickets%20for%20%242%2C750%20for%20the%20Corner%20Clubs%20section%20and%20%243%2C000%20for%20the%20Cabanas%20section.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20stark%20differences%20in%20pricing%20and%20demand%20between%20matches%20and%20they%20can%20be%20seen%20with%20Saturday's%20Netherlands-South%20Africa%20match%20at%20the%20same%20venue%3A%20Tickets%20were%20available%20for%20between%20%24120%20for%20Premium%20and%20%24700%20for%20Premium%20Club%20sections%20on%20the%20ICC%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETickets%20for%20the%20upcoming%20India-US%20match%20on%20Wednesday%20were%20listed%20at%20%24300%20for%20Premium%2C%20%241%2C000%20for%20Premium%20Club%20Lounge%2C%20Cabanas%20for%20%241%2C350%2C%20and%20Diamond%20Club%20for%20%247%2C500.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EICC%20began%20selling%20tickets%20through%20what%20it%20called%20a%20%E2%80%9Cpublic%20ballot%E2%80%9D%2C%20a%20process%20in%20which%20fans%20applied%20for%20tickets%20andsome%20were%20randomly%20selected%20to%20get%20them%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EICC%20said%20that%20the%20demand%20for%20the%20India-Pakistan%20match%20tickets%20at%20the%2034%2C000-capacity%20stadium%20exceeded%20supply%20by%20200%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20those%20who%20got%20tickets%20at%20the%20ballot%2C%20or%20the%20open%20online%20sales%20later%20in%20February%20and%20in%20April%20are%20trying%20to%20make%20a%20hefty%20quick%20buck%20on%20the%20resale%20markets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStubhub%2C%20Viagogo%20and%20such%20sites%20act%20as%20middlemen%20charging%20a%20fee%20to%20the%20seller%20and%20buyer%20based%20on%20the%20value%20of%20the%20ticket%20and%20guaranteeing%20the%20transaction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20despite%20the%20hype%20of%20the%20%24175%2C400%20demand%20for%20a%20ticket%2C%20the%20asking%20prices%20on%20the%20secondary%20markets%20mostly%20ranged%20between%20%24700%20and%20%241%2C000%2C%20still%20a%20big%20markup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20these%20were%20selling%20and%20indicating%20the%20closed%20transactions%20a%20slash%20appeared%20through%20the%20listing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20costliest%20listing%20on%20Stubhub%20was%20for%20%2418%2C000%20in%20Section%20101.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20followed%20by%20one%20for%20%2413%2C%20496%20in%20the%20Diamond%20section%2C%20where%20the%20lister%20said%20it%20included%20privileges%20like%20free%20VIP%20parking%2C%20and%20complimentary%20%E2%80%9Cunlimited%20food%20and%20drinks%20(beer%2C%20wine%20and%20liquor)%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EViagogo%20had%20a%20%246%2C700%20listing%20for%20a%20Diamond%20Club%20seat.%20Most%20tickets%20on%20it%20had%20an%20asking%20price%20between%20the%20%24500s%20and%20low%20%24700s.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Vividseats%2C%20the%20costliest%20listing%20was%20%248%2C013%20and%20the%20cheapest%20%24693.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717837200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2F3mcdaeqg_rohit-sharma-babar-azam-afp_625x300_09_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Findia-vs-pakistan-t20-world-cup-ticket-price-175-400-seat-listed-on-resale-market-5843781%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22New%20York%2C%20June%208%20(IANS)%20Is%20there%20something%20magical%20about%20Seat%2030%20in%20Row%2020%20of%20Section%20252%20at%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%20stadium%20in%20East%20Meadow%3F%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Findia-vs-pakistan-t20-world-cup-ticket-price-175-400-seat-listed-on-resale-market-5843781%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Findia-vs-pakistan-t20-world-cup-ticket-price-175-400-seat-listed-on-resale-market-5843781%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Findia-vs-pakistan-t20-world-cup-ticket-price-175-400-seat-listed-on-resale-market-5843781%2Famp%2F1%22