20around%20much.%20On%20the%20weekends%20when%20we%20went%20to%20my%20mom's%20house%2C%20I%20felt%20a%20responsibility%20to%20take%20care%20of%20my%20sister%2C%20because%20my%20mom%20wasn't%20a%20good%20caretaker.%20When%20we%20stayed%20at%20home%2C%20I%20became%20a%20second%20set%20of%20hands%20to%20help%20my%20dad%20and%20granny%20change%20diapers%2C%20warm%20bottles%2C%20and%20read%20bedtime%20stories.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBy%20the%20time%20my%20half-brother%20came%20along%2C%20who%20was%20from%20another%20relationship%20my%20dad%20had%2C%20I%20had%20just%20turned%2016.%20Though%20I%20was%20older%2C%20smarter%2C%20and%20more%20capable%20of%20helping%20with%20his%20care%2C%20I%20also%20had%20a%20busier%20social%20life%20and%20a%20huge%20school%20workload%20full%20of%20AP%20classes%2C%20so%20I%20couldn't%20be%20as%20hands-on.%20However%2C%20I%20would%20still%20do%20things%20like%20babysit%20and%20help%20to%20calm%20down%20his%20crying%20when%20he%20had%20colic.%20It%20was%20then%20that%20I%20first%20had%20an%20inkling%20that%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwoman-doesnt-want-children-told-shed-change-her-mind-2022-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eraising%20kids%20wasn't%20in%20the%20cards%20for%20me%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUnlike%20all%20of%20my%20other%20friends%20at%20school%2C%20who%20told%20me%20about%20their%20daydreams%20of%20having%20multiple%20children%20and%20being%20a%20super-mom%2C%20I%20just%20didn't%20long%20for%20it%20the%20way%20that%20they%20did.%20To%20me%2C%20it%20always%20felt%20more%20like%20an%20expectation%20from%20society%20rather%20than%20something%20that%20would%20actually%20be%20fulfilling%20for%20me.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hayley%20Folk%20with%20her%20sister%20when%20they%20were%20young.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.co