%20or%2015%20years.%20Tenants%20cannot%20remove%20the%20setup%20to%20take%20it%20somewhere%20else%20because%20it%20will%20again%20involve%20paperwork%20and%20installation%20costs.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%2212%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ELet%E2%80%99s%20assume%20the%20monthly%20power%20expenses%20to%20be%20Rs%202%2C500%20and%20the%20cost%20of%20installation%20and%20inverter%20(with%20a%2010-year%20warranty)%20to%20be%20Rs%201.5%20lakh.%20So%2C%20for%20a%2015-year%20contract%2C%20the%20return%20on%20investment%20will%20be%20generated%20only%20after%20five%20years%20and%20residents%20can%20avail%20of%20eight%20years%20of%20free%20electricity%20provided%20the%20inverter%20lasts%20for%20say%2013%20years.%20Later%20on%2C%20the%20landlord%20will%20incur%20the%20capital%20cost%20for%20the%20new%20inverter.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%2213%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHighlighting%20the%20challenges%20on%20the%20terrace%20and%20balconies%2C%20Harish%20mentions%20that%20residents%20will%20have%20to%20bear%20metre%20and%20wiring%20expenses%20that%20can%20go%20up%20to%20Rs%201%20lakh.%20Using%20balconies%20could%20not%20be%20very%20feasible%20if%20the%20energy%20generation%20will%20be%20small-scale%20compared%20to%20the%20requirement.%20In%20the%20case%20of%20balconies%2C%20there%20are%20safety%20risks%20from%20extreme%20weather%20events%20like%20lightning%20strikes%2C%20strong%20winds%2C%20and%20cyclones%20that%20can%20damage%20the%20panels.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EKiran%20points%20out%20that%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20lot%20of%20paperwork%20involved%20with%20the%20concerned%20electricity%20boards.%20For%20instance%2C%20the%20contract%20term%20with%20the%20concerned%20electricity%20provider%20and%20the%20subsidy.%20The%20service%20provider%20and%20the%20solar%20installation%20companies%20will%20help%20do%20the%20paperwork%20but%20ensure%20that%20you%20keep%20a%20copy%20of%20all%20the%20documents.%3C%2F