D%20he%20says%20with%20conviction.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20a%20surgeon%2C%20I%20am%20deeply%20humbled%20to%20be%20part%20of%20this%20programme.%20During%20organ%20donations%2C%20I%20witness%20both%20ends%20of%20the%20spectrum%20%E2%80%93%20the%20profound%20grief%20of%20losing%20a%20loved%20one%20and%20the%20overwhelming%20joy%20and%20hope%20when%20a%20family%20member%20receives%20an%20organ.%20It%20truly%20embodies%20the%20cycle%20of%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717422349000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FLaunch-of-MOHAN-Foundation-in-1997-in-Chennai-1717420294.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D351914%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Dr%20Sunil%20Shroff%2C%20a%20renal%20transplant%20surgeon%2C%20established%20the%20MOHAN%20Foundation%20in%201997%20after%20facing%20criticism%20abroad%20over%20the%20rising%20kidney%20transplant%20scams%20in%20India.%20His%20organisation%20educates%20and%20empowers%20people%20to%20take%20the%20organ%20donation%20pledge.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Aruna%20Raghuram%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F351914%2Forgan-donation-in-india-donor-mohan-foundation-dr-sunil-shroff-kbc-episode-kidney-transplant%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22For%20Just%20Rs%20350%2C%20%23DonateAnUmbrella%20to%20Street%20Vendors%20Working%20in%20Extreme%20Heatwaves%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%9CNo%20one%20thinks%20like%20this%20for%20us%3B%20we%20have%20just%20gotten%20used%20to%20the%20heat%20every%20year.%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20A%20Delhi%20Street%20Vendor%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EImagine%2