%20have%20a%20roof%20over%20our%20heads.%20I%20was%20able%20to%20make%20a%20pucca%20house%20for%20my%20family.%20I%20remember%20my%20mother%20and%20%3Cem%3Edadi%20%3C%2Fem%3E(grandmother)%20would%20make%20this%20salt%20and%20I%20would%20relish%20it%20with%20%3Cem%3Eroti%3C%2Fem%3E.%20They%20taught%20me%20the%20procedure%20as%20well%20but%20I%20had%20never%20imagined%20this%20would%20become%20a%20source%20of%20livelihood%20to%20me%20later%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%2036-year-old%2C%20who%20now%20earns%20up%20to%20Rs%2010%2C000%20per%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESelling%20the%20flavoured%20salt%20has%20changed%20not%20only%20the%20lives%20of%20these%20rural%20women%20but%20also%20Sandeep%2C%20who%20was%20once%20thrown%20out%20of%20his%20home%20for%20bringing%20disgrace%20to%20the%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20father%20was%20in%20the%20Army.%20When%20I%20told%20my%20family%20that%20I%20intended%20to%20sell%20salt%2C%20they%20were%20disappointed%20in%20me.%20My%20relatives%20mocked%20us%20and%20asked%20me%20to%20do%20better%20jobs.%20For%20Army%20persons%2C%20dignity%20is%20very%20prestigious%20and%20no%20one%20found%20dignity%20in%20the%20idea%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F257903%2Futtarakhand-startup-himshakti-pahadi-namak-pink-salt-harshit-sahdev-ancient-food-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eselling%20salts%3C%2Fa%3E.%20My%20family%20thought%20that%20I%20was%20heading%20in%20the%20wrong%20direction%20and%20that%20I%20was%20possessed%20by%20some%20hill%20ghost!%E2%80%9D%20he%20laughs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20believed%20me%20only%20after%20six%20months%20when%20my%20work%20was%20featured%20in%20the%20news.%20Meanwhile%2C%20my%20friends%2C%20who%20are%20in%20the%20US%2C%20are%20buying%20luxurious%20cars.%20Often%2C%20they%20asked%20me%20to%20join%20them%20and%20earn%20handsome%20salaries.%20But%20here%2C%20when%20I%20see%20happy%20families%20getting%20financial%20independence%20through%20our%20work%2C%20it%20motivates%20me%20to%20work%20further.%20No%20other%20achievement%20could%20give%20us%20the%20contentment%20we%20experience%20through%20this%20work.%20Every%20night%2C%20I%20sleep%20well%20knowing%2080%20families%20are%20sleeping%20peacefully%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20photos%3A%20HimFla.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716976330000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FHimFla-2-1716968175.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D351421%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sandeep%20Pandey%E2%80%99s%20dreams%20of%20opening%20a%20restaurant%20were%20shattered%20by%20the%202013%20Uttarakhand%20floods.%20Later%2C%20with%20his%20childhood%20friends%20Sourabh%20Pant%20and%20Yogendra%20Singh%2C%20he%20founded%20HimFla%2C%20a%20startup%20selling%20Uttarakhand's%20traditional%20%E2%80%98pahadi%E2%80%99%20salt.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F351421%2Fhimfla-himalayan-flavours-pahadi-salt-pisyun-loon-sandeep-pandey-sourabh-pant-yogendra-singh-uttarakhand%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%227%20Techies%20Who%20Engineered%20Success%20in%20Sustainable%20Tourism%20With%20Their%20Dreamy%20Homestays%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EYears%20ago%2C%20seven%20individuals%20set%20out%20to%20pursue%20engineering%20and%20other%20tech-related%20fields.%20But%20mid-journey%2C%20they%20had%20a%20calling%20%E2%80%94%20a%20strong%20urge%20to%20adopt%20a%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F348074%2Fsustainable-home-wayanad-kerala-george-ramapuram-earthitects-hillside-jungle-home-nature%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20sustainable%20lifestyle%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20build%20a%20home%